 <h2>Why did I develop pocket button firefox extension?</h2>

    <h3>On mobile phones, you have to go through layers of menus to save web pages to pocket</h3>
    <p>It would be nice if there was a pocket button for the web page. At first I developed a <a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/show-pocket-button/">Show Pocket Button</a>, which was fixed in a web page, and later integrated it into the <a href="index.html">Show Close Tab Button</a>. One of the problems is that after editing the tag, it is very troublesome to close the window.</p>

    <h3>Click Comparison</h3>
    <h4>
	    Number of clicks to save the web page to pocket:5</h4>
